data.description: A one-of-a-kind custom home with breathtaking views on Mount Helix, near Rancho San Diego. This home was thoughtfully designed by Jay Foltz to maximize the awe-inspiring views that surround it.  Tucked away at the end of a peaceful cul-de-sac, this property offers an array of impressive features.  Inside, you'll discover a beautifully remodeled kitchen, an updated primary suite conveniently located on the entry level, and a second bedroom suite downstairs.   With spacious rooms featuring expansive windows, multiple balconies and patios, and an abundance of natural light, you'll always feel connected to the stunning outdoor scenery.  The property has numerous updates, including a newly installed HVAC system with 14 Seer rating, new carpet throughout, energy-efficient windows, a relaxing dry sauna, and high-end kitchen and bathroom remodels.   Nestled on a generously sized lot of approximately 3/4 of an acre, the property boasts a fenced backyard, fruit trees, several levels of decks and patios, which all complemented the gorgeous panoramic views. Additionally, the two-car garage offers direct access to the house, plus there's an oversized carport and room for large vehicles, making parking a breeze.  This house was designed with versatility in mind, catering to various lifestyles. Whether you're looking for intimate gatherings, moments of tranquility, or spacious entertaining, this property has you covered. It's well-suited for multi-generational living, offering a range of possibilities for its fortunate new owner.
